https://leetcode.com/problems/accounts-merge/

8.4 Dijkstraâ€™s Algorithm (Shortest Path)
What it is:
Greedy algorithm using a min-heap to find the shortest path from a source to all nodes (non-negative weights).

Used for:

Shortest path problems
Weighted graphs
Minimum cost / time problems
